  "description": "<p></p><p>Key Responsibilities</p><p>Administrative & Operations Support</p><p>•\tProvide general administrative support including scheduling, coordination of meetings, and internal arrangements</p><p>•\tSupport day-to-day operational matters and ad-hoc administrative requests</p><p>•\tManage documentation and filing systems to ensure accurate and organized records</p><p>•\tAssist with onboarding processes and related administrative arrangements</p><p></p><p>Supplies & Logistics</p><p>•\tSupport procurement and coordination of office supplies and materials</p><p>•\tAssist in managing logistical arrangements for internal needs and activities</p><p></p><p>Marketing & Design</p><p>•\tPrepare presentation decks for meetings and internal use</p><p>•\tDevelop marketing materials for social media and internal communications</p><p>•\tDesign materials for company activities and events</p><p>•\tBuild branding across materials and platforms</p><p></p><p>Basic Accounts Support</p><p>•\tTrack operational and marketing-related expenditure</p><p>•\tMaintain records for spending and reimbursements</p><p>•\tSupport basic accounts-related administrative processes</p>",
